{{orphan|date=September 2016}} {{Infobox person | name = Bella Miranda | website = {{url|www.bellamiranda.com}} | image = BellaMiranda.jpg | caption = Miranda at an event in Texas | birthname = | birth_date = | birth_place = | age = | death_date = | death_place = | education = | occupation = Entrepreneur, executive business coach, advisor and life coach | party = | alias = | gender = | status = | title = | family = | spouse = | children = | relatives = | nationality = | religion = | salary = | networth = | credits = | agent = }} '''Bella Miranda''' is an [[Americans|American]] [[Coaching|life coach]] to several famous people.{{Who|date=September 2016}}<ref name="Forbes">{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/meggentaylor/2016/06/07/4-tips-to-find-your-success-from-life-coach-bella-miranda/#3edc0bcb46d0|title=4 Tips To Find Your Success From Life-Coach, Bella Miranda|last=Taylor|first=Meggen|date=7 June 2016|website=|publisher=[[Forbes]]|access-date=27 September 2016}}</ref><ref name="Huffington">{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/how-to-harness-the-power-of-body-language_us_57d44cb4e4b0273330ac420a|title=How To Harness The Power of Body Language|first1=Bella|last1=Mir|first2=A.|last2=Executive|first3=Celebrity Life|last3=Coach|first4=Inspirational|last4=Speaker|first5=|last5=Author|date=10 September 2016|publisher=[[Huffingtonpost]]}}</ref>
==Early life and background== Miranda was born in [[Texas, United States]]. Miranda is an advisor, executive business coach, executive strategic coach and life coach to a wide array of influential people in Fortune 100 companies, space industries, world leaders, CEOs, boards of directors and the entertainment industry. She is a captivating public speaker and author of her upcoming book based on her training philosophies and success.
Miranda is currently working with certain commercial and private space companies to help the human population become an interplanetary species. Miranda is currently a sponsor for [[List of astronauts by year of selection#Association of Spaceflight Professionals|Association of Spaceflight Professionals]], is on the patrons board and observer on the board of directors for the Commercial Spaceflight Federation. Miranda sits on the advisory board for Space For Humanity and is an executive advisor for Arch Mission. Miranda has been featured in ''Forbes'', ''Huffington Post'' and more for her teachings and successes.<ref name="huffingtonpost.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/author/thebellamiranda-155|title=Bella Miranda profile|publisher=[[Huffingtonpost]]}}</ref><ref name="TBN">{{cite web|last1=Staff reporter|title=Four Ideas To Discover Your Success From Life-Coach, Bella Miranda|url=http://business.truebreakingnews.com/2016/06/07/four-ideas-to-discover-your-success-from-life-coach-bella-miranda/|website=True Breaking News|accessdate=27 September 2016}}</ref>
